An unclosed nowiki swallows the rest inline: literal
\textquotesingle\textquotesingle\textquotesingle text\textquotesingle\textquotesingle\textquotesingle{}
and {[}{[}links{]}{]} until the end.

And separately, an unclosed pre block:

\begin{verbatim}
preformatted content
that has no closing tag
so it runs to the end of input
\end{verbatim}
